  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Trobitz.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, one of the reasons that I didn't speak too much about my brother Al in Bergen-Belsen is because we did not see each other that much while there.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As I said, he was with my brother in the men's section, and I was with my mother in the women's section.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We did get glimpses of each other now and then, particularly when we were standing on appell.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I do recall one incident where my brother was given an apple by a soldier who was on guard.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, there were always guards surrounding us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this must have been a particularly long day of standing on appell.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was a young guard, a young man, who gave my brother an apple.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, he was jeopardizing his own life by doing so.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my brother, I remember, sharing that apple into I don't know how many little pieces.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was just an incident that that will always be with us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it just goes to show that despite the horror and the horrendous treatment that we all received by the-- the Germans, that one must not generalize.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It goes to show that there are exceptions.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And here was this one young man who was really [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] endangering his own life by giving this one apple.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He just probably felt the need to do something good and to help in his own way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It-- it-- again, I think something like that gave us a little bit of hope, and-- and it just helped us along.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
